            <div type="a">
                <column>05</column>
                <head>The Situation</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The paper asserts that news from across the country shows that "the
                    Radicals are getting scared and the honest, common sense of the masses North are
                    coming into play. If we Southern people are only united, our future is secure."</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
